automobile, electrical appliances, textile, metallurgy, and
chemical industries, discussed how to accelerate the growth of
large state-owned enterprises by optimizing the use of resources
and improving management efficiency.
</P>
<P>
Shanghai sends abroad entrepreneurs and government officials
every year to learn new methods of running large businesses, Jiang
said, and foreign advisors are also invited to work in the city.
