prepared well defensively. "We had too many faults in the
defensive position," he added.
</P>
<P>
He also regretted that injuries restricted the performance of
his team.
</P>
<P>
The winner of the group comprising Cameroun, Egypt and Nigeria
will qualify for the World Championship in Japan in November this
year. 
