<HEADLINE> Kenyan Lagat Wins Berlin Marathon </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BERLIN, September 28 (Xinhua) -- Kenyan runners showed their
domination in marathon by sweeping the 1-2-3 finish and a fourth
place in the 24th annual Berlin Marathon on Sunday.
</P>
<P>
