<HEADLINE> Italy, Albania to Cooperate in Crime Fighting </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
ROME, September 27 (Xinhua) -- Italy and Albania will intensify
their collaboration in fighting against crimes, especially drug
trafficking and arms smuggling, Italian national anti-Mafia
