</P>
<P>
He said that he received a request from the Albanian national
prosecutor for cooperation in dealing with criminal organizations
operating between the two countries.
</P>
<P>
He said that there has been a recent increase in the amount of
drugs and arms being smuggled into Italy from across the Adriatic
Sea.
</P>
<P>
The drugs smuggled into Italy by Albanian drug traffickers in
last four months doubled that of the first four months of this
year, he said.
</P>
<P>
In the northeastern Italian city of Trieste, police today
seized 29 kilograms of marijuana and arrested 11 Albanians and
Italians, who were suspected to use illegal immigrants to smuggle
drugs into Italy from Albania.
</P>
<P>
Meanwhile, 11 Albanians were caught trying to enter Italy
illegally aboard a ferry boat in Brindisi. They were sent back to
Albania later. 
</P>
</TEXT>
</BODY>
</DOC>
